### About Me
This GitHub contains the various personal projects that I have worked on throughout my programming career. I'm currently a Sophomore studying Computer Science at the University of Arizona. I am most comfortable in the Java programming language and can understand basic C++. My interests include theoretical computer science, operating systems, and compilers along with a curiosity in graphics.

Tools that I'm comfortable using:

* Java
* Eclipse
* Eclemma (Code Coverage tool)
* Git
* Linux
